I major in Information Engineering at College of Information Science and Electronic Engineering and minor in the Advanced Honor Class of Engineering Education (ACEE) in Chu Kochen Honors College. Currently, I’m doing my Bachelor’s thesis internship on machine learning and biomedical imaging at Yale Univeristy, supervised by Prof. James Duncan.
